{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":5},{"title":2,"date":3,"citation":4},"Hellenistic Sicilian real estate contracts inscribed on lead tablets: new readings and implications for the economic independence of women","2016","\u003Cspan>Randall Souza, ‘Hellenistic Sicilian Real Estate Contracts Inscribed on Lead Tablets: New Readings and Implications for the Economic Independence of Women’, \u003Ci>Zeitschrift Fūr Papyrologie Und Epigraphik\u003C/i> 197 (2016): 149–66\u003C/span>",[6,104,142],{"file":7,"uri":7,"title":8,"status":9,"editionAuthor":11,"type":12,"objectType":16,"material":20,"condition":24,"layoutDesc":26,"handNote":35,"date":37,"places":42,"geo":51,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":58,"idno":62,"textLang":64,"facsimile":68,"provenance":44,"letterHeights":75,"publications":76,"zotero":83,"keywords":90,"html":103},"ISic030001","Contract for the sale of a house",{"_":10},"draft",null,{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},"Private contract","#function.legal.private.contract","https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/375.html",{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},"lamina","#object.lamina","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/145.html",{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},"Lead","#material.metal.lead","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/108.html",{"ana":25},"#condition.damaged condition.fragments.contiguous",{"layout":27},{"p":28,"rs":29,"damage":33},"The lines of text begin at the left edge of the sheet and run across to the right edge without margins. Although the original upper edge of the tablet is lost, the beginning of the text is likely preserved; it is unclear what the top margin was. The bottom margin is approximately as tall as is the text itself, i.e. the text ends around the midpoint of the sheet as currently preserved. The first four lines fill the width of the sheet and when the line ends in the middle of a word either the final letters are squeezed in (L.1) or the word is interrupted (L.3).",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},"engraved","#execution.engraved","https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/3.html",{"ana":34},"#text_condition.incomplete",{"dimensions":36},[11,11],{"_":38,"notBefore":39,"notAfter":40,"evidence":41},"2nd century BCE",-200,-101,"lettering",[43,47],{"_":44,"type":45,"ref":46},"Morgantina","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462372",{"_":48,"type":49,"ref":50},"Aidone","modern","http://www.geonames.org/6537793/aidone.html",[52],[53,54],37.43067,14.47945,"Italy","Sicily","Ragusa",{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},"Museo Archeologico Ibleo","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/091",{"type":63},"inventory",{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":67},"Ancient Greek","grc",[65],{"n":69,"url":70,"height":71,"width":72,"desc":73,"surfaceType":74},"screen","ISic030001_tiled.tif","2195px","3212px","Composite photo of the inscribed surface, R. Souza, courtesy Museo Regionale Interdisciplinare di Ragusa","front",[],[77,77,77,78,79,80,81,82],"Supplementum epigraphicum graecum, 1923-","Bulletin épigraphique, 1888-","Manganaro, 1989, Case e terra a Kamarina e Morgantina nel III–II sec. a.C.","Game, 2009, Actes de vente dans le monde grec. Témoignages épigraphiques des ventes immobilières","Dubois, 2008, IGDS2","Souza, 2016, Hellenistic Sicilian real estate contracts inscribed on lead tablets: new readings and implications for the economic independence of women",[84,84,84,85,86,87,88,89],"F2GG87EQ","77P5MNIR","SIK4QJV4","H87ZNHMA","SM2KDHZC","BKZKNUPN",[91,92,93,94,17,95,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030001","contract for the sale of a house",{"_":10},"private contract","lead","morgantina","aidone","italy","sicily","ragusa","museo archeologico ibleo","ancient greek","Text encoding: Randall Souza",{"file":105,"uri":105,"title":106,"status":107,"editionAuthor":11,"type":108,"objectType":109,"material":110,"condition":111,"layoutDesc":113,"handNote":118,"date":120,"places":124,"geo":128,"country":55,